<item>
            <title>[LU-8595] Interop: master&lt;-&gt;b2_8 : sanity test_133a fails with &quot;The counter for unlink on mds1 was not incremented&quot;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8595</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Saurabh Tandan &amp;lt;saurabh.tandan@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/357e40cc-70c8-11e6-8afd-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/357e40cc-70c8-11e6-8afd-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_133a failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;The counter for unlink on mds1 was not incremented
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test log:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity test 133a: Verifying MDT stats ============================================================= 02:14:43 (1472696083)
CMD: trevis-42vm7 /usr/sbin/lctl list_param mdt.*.rename_stats
mdt.lustre-MDT0000.rename_stats
CMD: trevis-42vm7 /usr/sbin/lctl set_param mdt.*.md_stats=clear
mdt.lustre-MDT0000.md_stats=clear
CMD: trevis-42vm8 /usr/sbin/lctl set_param obdfilter.*.stats=clear
obdfilter.lustre-OST0000.stats=clear
obdfilter.lustre-OST0001.stats=clear
obdfilter.lustre-OST0002.stats=clear
obdfilter.lustre-OST0003.stats=clear
obdfilter.lustre-OST0004.stats=clear
obdfilter.lustre-OST0005.stats=clear
obdfilter.lustre-OST0006.stats=clear
CMD: trevis-42vm7 /usr/sbin/lctl get_param mdt.lustre-MDT0000.md_stats
mkdir 1 samples [reqs]
CMD: trevis-42vm7 /usr/sbin/lctl get_param mdt.lustre-MDT0000.md_stats
open 1 samples [reqs]
CMD: trevis-42vm7 /usr/sbin/lctl get_param mdt.lustre-MDT0000.md_stats
close 1 samples [reqs]
CMD: trevis-42vm7 /usr/sbin/lctl get_param mdt.lustre-MDT0000.md_stats

 sanity test_133a: @@@@@@ FAIL: The counter for unlink on mds1 was not incremented 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;According to maloo this issue was first seen first on b2_8_fe branch on 2016-06-20&lt;/p&gt;</description>
